    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="intro-box">
            <p><strong>Company:</strong> PETFRIENDS (Pty) Ltd ("we", "us", "our")</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> MyPetFriends (the "Site")</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>PETFRIENDS (Pty) Ltd is committed to protecting your personal information and complying with the Protection of Personal Information Act, 4 of 2013 ("POPIA").</p>
            <p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, share, and protect your personal information when you use our website or any related services.</p>
            <p>By using our Site, you consent to the practices described in this Policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. What personal information we collect</h2>
            <p>We collect the following categories of personal information:</p>
            
            <h3>2.1 Personal identification details</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Full name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Cell phone number</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2.2 Profile & experience information (for sitters)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Years of pet-sitting experience</li>
                <li>Number of pets owned</li>
                <li>Number of pets previously cared for</li>
                <li>Personal biography</li>
                <li>Personal profile pictures</li>
                <li>Home suburb</li>
                <li>Pet-care services offered</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2.3 Reviews and ratings</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Written reviews</li>
                <li>Star ratings</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2.4 Booking information (when a booking request is submitted)</h3>
            <p>When a user submits a booking request, we collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Pet owner's full name</li>
                <li>Pet's name</li>
                <li>Dates and duration of care needed</li>
                <li>The user's message to the sitter</li>
                <li>Any additional instructions or notes</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This information is shared only with the sitter selected by the user.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. How we collect information</h2>
            <p>We collect information when you:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Create a sitter profile</li>
                <li>Join our waitlist or contact us</li>
                <li>Submit or respond to a booking request</li>
                <li>Upload profile details or images</li>
                <li>Leave a review</li>
                <li>Interact with our platform</li>
                <li>Communicate with us via the website, email, or forms</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Why we collect your information (Purpose of processing)</h2>
            <p>We process personal information to:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Create and display sitter profiles</li>
                <li>Connect pet owners with pet sitters</li>
                <li>Facilitate booking requests and scheduling</li>
                <li>Allow sitters to review and respond to booking requests</li>
                <li>Enable communication between pet owners and sitters</li>
                <li>Provide customer support</li>
                <li>Improve platform functionality and safety</li>
                <li>Maintain records for operational and security purposes</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>We do not sell your personal information.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Legal basis for processing</h2>
            <p>Under POPIA, we process your information based on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your consent</li>
                <li>Legitimate business interests (operating a pet-sitting connection platform)</li>
                <li>Performance of services requested by you</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You may withdraw consent at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Who we share your information with</h2>
            
            <h3>6.1 Sitters (for bookings)</h3>
            <p>If you submit a booking request, your booking details (name, pet name, dates, message) are shared only with the sitter you selected.</p>

            <h3>6.2 Public profile visibility</h3>
            <p>Sitters' profile information (bio, suburb, photos, experience, services offered) may be visible to pet owners on the Site.</p>

            <h3>6.3 Service providers</h3>
            <p>We may share information with trusted service providers who assist with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website hosting</li>
                <li>Email notifications</li>
                <li>Analytics</li>
                <li>Data storage</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All providers are required to comply with POPIA.</p>
            <p><strong>We do not share your data with advertisers.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. How we store and protect personal information</h2>
            <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational safeguards, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Secure servers</li>
                <li>Encrypted connections (HTTPS)</li>
                <li>Access controls</li>
                <li>Data minimisation</li>
                <li>Restricted staff access</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Booking information is accessible only to PETFRIENDS administration and the sitter involved.</p>
            <p>We retain data only as long as necessary for operational, legal, or security reasons.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>8. Cookies and tracking</h2>
            <p>The Site may use cookies or analytics tools to improve user experience.</p>
            <p>No personally identifying information is collected through cookies.</p>
            <p>You may disable cookies through your browser.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>9. Children's information</h2>
            <p>We do not knowingly collect information from anyone under 18.</p>
            <p>If we become aware that a minor has submitted personal information, we will delete it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>10. Your POPIA rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <div class="rights-box">
                <ul>
                    <li>Access your personal information</li>
                    <li>Correct or update your information</li>
                    <li>Request deletion</li>
                    <li>Withdraw consent</li>
                    <li>Object to processing</li>
                    <li>Lodge a complaint with the Information Regulator</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at the email below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>11. Updates to this Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.</p>
            <p>Changes will be posted with an updated "Last Revised" date.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-box">
            <h3>12. Contact Information</h3>
            <p>For any privacy-related queries:</p>
